ing: 1 rotisserie chicken, meat removed and chopped
salt and ground black pepper to taste
des: "Rotisserie chicken soft tacos made with homemade flour tortillas and pico de gallo."
ins: Heat vegetable oil in a skillet over medium heat; cook and stir chicken, chili powder, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper together in the hot oil until chicken is heated through, about 10 minutes. Spoon chicken mixture onto each tortilla and top with pico de gallo and Mexican cheese blend.
